cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on image-to-image translation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) and the proposed Discriminative Region Proposal Adversarial Networks (DRPANs) also suggests that this paper could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of patch discriminators and revisers could also suggest that this paper could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
